This project project does not pretend to be a Full Point Of Sale. It's target is limited.

There will be 2 ways of accessing the app. short version

General Customers : 
 - website_url 
	- Similar to a e-commerce page
	- User creates account, checkouts out products, choose from 2 available payment methods.

Employees : 
 - store_url - This will be the Point Of Sale
 - Add products to cart
 - Checkout, ask client for details and submit order. 
 - Generate PDF from order. This will generate login information for client to access website_url.
 - Order is associated to employee and shop (there can be various shops)

Gems:

gem 'activeadmin'
gem 'formtastic'
gem 'devise'
gem 'twitter-bootstrap-rails'
